### Category Management Tests
### Test CRUD operations cho product categories

@gatewayUrl = http://localhost:3000

@token = {{loginAdmin.response.body.accessToken}}

### 1. List All Categories
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/categories?page=1&pageSize=20

### 2. Search Categories
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/categories?q=điện&page=1&pageSize=10

### 3. Create Parent Category
# @name createParentCategory
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Điện tử",
  "slug": "dien-tu",
  "description": "Các sản phẩm điện tử"
}

### 4. Create Child Category
# @name createChildCategory
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Điện thoại",
  "slug": "dien-thoai",
  "description": "Điện thoại di động",
  "parentId": "{{createParentCategory.response.body.id}}"
}

### 5. Get Category by ID (with children)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/categories/{{createParentCategory.response.body.id}}

### 6. Get Category by Slug
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/categories/slug/dien-tu

### 7. List Categories by Parent
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/categories?parentSlug=dien-tu

### 8. Update Category
PUT {{gatewayUrl}}/categories/{{createChildCategory.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Điện thoại thông minh",
  "description": "Smartphone cao cấp"
}

### 9. Delete Category (expect error if has children/products)
DELETE {{gatewayUrl}}/categories/{{createChildCategory.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. List without authentication (public endpoint)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/categories